      "span_text": "18 G␥ 2 was inserted into this construct downstream the IRES to obtain bicistronic mRNA. Recombinant adenoviruses were generated by homologous recombination with the adenoviral backbone vector pAd-Easy-1.  Adenoviruses encoding for GFP alone and the long form of rat G␣ s has been described. 7",
